<p>

<b>Romesco</b>, (central catalan pronunciation <b>romescu</b>), is a sauce originating in <site wordnetid="108651247" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<village wordnetid="108672738" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../704/59704.xml">
Tarragona</link></village>
</site>
, <region wordnetid="108630039" confidence="0.8">
<location wordnetid="100027167" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../822/6822.xml">
Catalonia</link></location>
</region>
, <system wordnetid="108435388" confidence="0.8">
<economy wordnetid="108366753" confidence="0.8">
<group wordnetid="100031264" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../667/26667.xml">
Spain</link></group>
</economy>
</system>
, that is typically made from  <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../064/1064.xml">
almond</link>s and/or <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../546/484546.xml">
hazelnut</link>s, roasted <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../469/50469.xml">
garlic</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../478/22478.xml">
olive oil</link> and  <link>
nyores</link> - small, dried <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../979/55979.xml">
red peppers</link>.  Other common ingredients include roasted <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../234/9940234.xml">
tomato</link>es, red wine <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../762/32762.xml">
vinegar</link> and <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../258/51258.xml">
onion</link>. Leaves of fennel or mint may be added, particularly if served with <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../587/4699587.xml">
fish</link> or <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../885/585885.xml">
escargot</link>. It is perhaps most often served with <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../866/26866.xml">
seafood</link>, but can also be served with a wide variety of other foods including <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../197/23197.xml">
poultry</link> and <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../492/5791492.xml">
vegetables</link>, particularly <link>
calçot</link>s.</p>

